法 （出40題單選，儘量出融合型、進階題型，不用標出主題，把一段全部文法主題混合在一起）\n4. 題組題（包括閱測、克漏字文章型的題目，出四個題組）\n\n3跟4題目來源可以是題庫、歷屆試題、自修、會考題、自出題型皆可，建議是比較有程度或考點的題目，有別於平常的小考或週考題。\n\n預計順序以及分工⬇️\n翰林單字 Ivy\n康軒單字  Ivy\n翰林課文 Christopher\n康軒課文Linda \n文法   Frank Lin \n題組 Chris\n答案 各自提供\n\n一次段考一個檔案，分別丟進去一二三段的資料夾","end":"","id":"mbu2n9boeog18niff2llvec5bg_google_com","isAllDay":true,"location":"","start":"2024-03-05","startObj":1709596800000,"title":"國一下一二三次小段複初稿"},{"description":"","end":"","id":"vn74490pa1kqs02l4p1gme07o8_google_com","isAllDay":true,"location":"","start":"2024-03-08","startObj":1709856000000,"title":"高一下高二下段複手冊排完"},{"description":"","end":"","id":"dh9h2lmr1t6iv9nmqrdoopav5o_google_com","isAllDay":true,"location":"","start":"2024-03-09","startObj":1709942400000,"title":"Linda上傳一下一段國中自修掃描檔"},{"description":"","end":"","id":"nfsu716ovdglj1ngbm8rl4cmhg_google_com","isAllDay":true,"location":"","start":"2024-03-12","startObj":1710201600000,"title":"國一下三次小段複排版完"},{"description":"打完上傳word檔到同一個資料夾 謝謝\n\nhttps://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1421CtZCLurujXJCUTOGF57XxfP8wikkb","end":"","id":"dbe8c2lnn52d9j20sknpr95uao_google_com","isAllDay":true,"location":"","start":"2024-03-13","startObj":1710288000000,"title":"Chris國三下模考打字"},{"description":"","end":"","id":"ciifab8nnipf3gqbr53ihkl4cg_google_com","isAllDay":true,"location":"","start":"2024-03-13","startObj":1710288000000,"title":"國一下三次小段複一校"},{"description":"","end":"","id":"1v160vqumgf8bfjocpeshg7k3o_google_com","isAllDay":true,"location":"","start":"2024-03-16","startObj":1710547200000,"title":"改高一下高二下段複手冊龍騰版"},{"description":"","end":"","id":"0ih28gg47nd8jqjp40a9bnrf8c_google_com","isAllDay":true,"location":"","start":"2024-03-18","startObj":1710720000000,"title":"改國一下三次小段複一校"},{"description":"(以下皆為整本)\n一下龍騰: Frank\n一下三民: Linda\n一下三民乙: Chris\n二下龍騰: Christopher\n二下三民: Demian","end":"","id":"gmbartendrjqf29vc26ld9vt4k_google_com","isAllDay":true,"location":"","start":"2024-03-22","startObj":1711065600000,"title":"高一二下段複手冊一校"},{"description":"","end":"